> </menuchoice>
    </term>
    <listitem>
      <para
>During the quiz you will be given the entries of Column 2 and asked to provide the corresponding Column 1 entries. </para>
    </listitem>
  </varlistentry>
</variablelist>
</sect1>
</chapter>

