>The Welcome Page</title>

<para
>When opening KWordQuiz, you will land on the welcome page. This page will list all the previously opened deck. Additionally it lets you create a new deck, open a deck from a file or download deck from the internet. Finally you can also choose which main mode you want to use. </para>

