      <phrase
>De meerkeuzevragen-sessie</phrase>
    </textobject>
  </mediaobject>
</screenshot>
<para
>Your choices are shown on the middle of the scren. Select the one you think is correct. Use <guibutton
>Check</guibutton
> to see if the answer is correct. If you have activated the automatic mode in <menuchoice
><guimenu
>Settings</guimenu
></menuchoice
> your selection is checked immediately. </para>
<para
>Select <guibutton
>Repeat Errors</guibutton
> to repeat the cards you have counted as incorrect. </para>
<para
>Select <guibutton
>Try again</guibutton
> to start the session from the beginning again. If you are using a random mode the cards will be reshuffled. </para>
<para
>The score section at the top of the screen shows the number of questions, the number of questions you have answered, the number of correct answers, and the number of incorrect answers. </para>
